1
00:00:00,615 --> 00:00:05,295
you're training a puppy. You can't just shout Fetch and expect it to understand

2
00:00:05,296 --> 00:00:07,335
perfectly. You need to give clear,

3
00:00:07,695 --> 00:00:11,155
specific instructions. Maybe even demonstrate what you want.

4
00:00:11,535 --> 00:00:14,415
Prompting AI is similar. Instead of vague requests,

5
00:00:15,055 --> 00:00:17,215
you provide detailed instructions, examples,

6
00:00:17,216 --> 00:00:20,455
or context to guide the AI towards the desired output.

7
00:00:20,655 --> 00:00:24,815
Think of a prompt as a a well-crafted command that tells the AI exactly

8
00:00:24,816 --> 00:00:27,295
what you want it to do. The better the prompt,

9
00:00:27,815 --> 00:00:31,435
the better the result. For example, instead of saying write a story,

10
00:00:31,795 --> 00:00:34,415
which is vague and unclear, you could say,

11
00:00:34,855 --> 00:00:38,135
write a short story about a cat who goes on an adventure in space,

12
00:00:38,755 --> 00:00:41,375
making sure to include elements of humor and surprise.

13
00:00:42,195 --> 00:00:44,475
This gives the AI a much clearer direction.

14
00:00:45,275 --> 00:00:48,475
Creating good prompts is just like following a recipe in the kitchen.

15
00:00:48,476 --> 00:00:51,455
Every great dish needs the right ingredients,

16
00:00:52,075 --> 00:00:54,975
proper measurements, and clear instructions.

17
00:00:55,275 --> 00:00:58,435
Our perfect prompt recipe has four essential ingredients,

18
00:00:58,835 --> 00:01:03,375
just like baking a cake. Each ingredient serves a specific purpose and must

19
00:01:03,376 --> 00:01:05,895
be measured correctly. First,

20
00:01:06,515 --> 00:01:08,795
clearly define your goal. In cooking,

21
00:01:09,175 --> 00:01:12,055
you decide what dish you want to make before gathering ingredients.

22
00:01:12,755 --> 00:01:16,555
With AI prompts, you must know exactly what you want the AI to create.

23
00:01:17,175 --> 00:01:22,015
Next, provide context. A chef considers available ingredients before cooking.

24
00:01:22,535 --> 00:01:26,995
Similarly, give the AI background information and relevant details to work with.

25
00:01:27,995 --> 00:01:32,075
Then specify the format. Just as you choose how to serve a meal in

26
00:01:32,076 --> 00:01:36,075
a bowl, on a plate, or in a glass, tell the AI exactly how

27
00:01:36,076 --> 00:01:38,555
you want your answer presented. Finally,

28
00:01:38,955 --> 00:01:43,115
use keywords. Secret spices transform a good dish into a great one.

29
00:01:43,116 --> 00:01:47,295
Similarly, specific keywords help the AI understand exactly what you want.

30
00:01:48,115 --> 00:01:51,535
Here's our recipe in action. This prompt has a clear goal,

31
00:01:52,015 --> 00:01:54,655
summarize an article. It specifies the format,

32
00:01:54,995 --> 00:01:59,535
three bullet points, and it uses keywords like focusing on main events and impact

33
00:01:59,536 --> 00:02:02,075
to guide the AI. Remember,

34
00:02:02,555 --> 00:02:06,735
experimentation is key. Just like a chef tweaking a recipe to perfection,

35
00:02:07,215 --> 00:02:10,215
try different prompts and see what works best. with practice,

36
00:02:10,615 --> 00:02:12,795
you'll master the art of prompt crafting.

37
00:02:13,395 --> 00:02:16,595
The world of prompt engineering is rapidly evolving,

38
00:02:16,895 --> 00:02:21,395
with exciting developments on the horizon that will change how we interact with AI

39
00:02:21,396 --> 00:02:24,635
systems. AI is getting smarter every day,

40
00:02:25,115 --> 00:02:29,935
and new techniques are constantly emerging to make our interactions more effective and

41
00:02:29,936 --> 00:02:34,495
intuitive. Another major advancement is multimodal prompting where

42
00:02:34,496 --> 00:02:39,095
you can combine text, images, audio and video in your prompts for richer

43
00:02:39,096 --> 00:02:41,735
and more comprehensive AI interactions.

44
00:02:42,495 --> 00:02:47,295
While some experts believe specialized prompt engineering roles might fade as AI becomes

45
00:02:47,296 --> 00:02:52,035
more intuitive, mastering the art of prompting will remain a valuable skill for

46
00:02:52,036 --> 00:02:55,155
anyone using AI in their daily work and life.
